HEADWORD: Exannulate
<hw>Ex*an"nu*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>ex-</ets> + <ets>annulate</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Having the sporangium destitute of a ring; -- said of certain
genera of ferns.</def>⟦br⟧
